description:
** Please note - this is just a placeholder, you cannot sign up here - currently we have closed this event to new signups, but you can go on the waiting list, or get in touch with us, if you are interested. We will let you know when there is a space **

This is a self-directed study group for everyone interested in improving their coding skills. It is going to be our first in-person event since March last year, so we are starting up small.

The goal is to help each other progress in our individual and/or group goals by providing space and time to meet other like-minded developers and ask questions.

What to bring: Your own laptop and complete dedication to respecting others

Attendance is currently limited to 10 people, if you registered and then can't make it anymore, please change your RSVP.
title: Coding Self-Study (Code101)
